/*
Required environment variables for production deployment on Render:

1. MONGODB_URI (or MONGO_URI) - MongoDB Atlas connection string
2. JWT_SECRET - Must match frontend SECRET_KEY
3. GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID - from Google Cloud Console
4. GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET - from Google Cloud Console
5. SMTP_USER - Gmail username or app password
6. SMTP_PASS - Gmail app password

Required variables:
- mongodb_uri
- jwt_secret
- google_client_id
- google_client_secret
- smtp_user
- smtp_pass

Set these in Render dashboard for production.